Create a main script with the following requirements:
 - recursively get a list of files which names are longer than specified length
 - sort that list of files according to the full name (beginning with the /)
 - report that list of files to the output on the screen and at the same time to some file
Input parameters:
 - directory name which has to be recursively search for files
 - natural number - minimum length for file name


Create preparation script which will create a random amount of directories(diffrent depth) and empty files with random names. Every directory should have different amount of files.
